This project is intended for automated weeding.
There are 4 components:
- An image aquisition device (camera or files on disk)
- A National Instruments RIO embedded controller
- An encoder attached to the RIO that emits pulses on wheel movements
- An emitter for treating weeds
- A laptop for performing image rocognition

Laptop executable: weeds.py
RIO executable: rio.py
Camera: Basler GigE or a collection of disk images

